Package: fitbitr
Type: Package
Title: Wraps The Fitbit API Into An Easy Functions
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Nick Strayer
Maintainer: Nick Strayer <n.strayer@vanderbilt.edu>
Description: Bundles conveneince tools for grabbing fitbit data from R. Functions are designed to work whether in an r script or a shiny app. 
    Also includes an interactive tagging tool for visualizing and tagging multiple days worth of heartrate and step data. 
